alized 1980s where the government outsources police work to private corporations and contractors. You play the role of a private intelligence investigator, making money by finding and selling information. Capture of the rampant serial killer carries a hefty bounty, but who knows what secrets you\u2019ll find along the way. In this world of secrets & lies, information is power, and the cards you hold are determined by how far you\u2019ll go to acquire it\u2026\n\nBreak into apartments, rifle through secret documents and hack security systems. The entire world is fully simulated. Each citizen has an apartment, a job, a daily routine, favorite things to do, places to go, and people to interact with. Uncover this knowledge and use it to your advantage!", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Science fiction"}, {"id": 23, "name": "Stealth"}, {"id": 33, "name": "Sandbox"}, {"id": 38, "name": "Open world"}, {"id": 43, "name": "Mystery"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/shadows-of-doubt", "videos": [{"id": 37195, "name": "Teaser", "video_id": "dI1UJNoQ8Mk", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dI1UJNoQ8Mk", "title": "Shadows of Doubt teaser | PC Gaming Show 2020", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dI1UJNoQ8Mk/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 69806, "name": "Gameplay Video", "video_id": "AkfbR3OmS1U", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AkfbR3OmS1U", "title": "Shadows of Doubt: August 2019 Pre-Alpha Gameplay", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AkfbR3OmS1U/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 122520, "name": "Release Date Trailer", "video_id": "Hz2ovrxAuN0", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hz2ovrxAuN0", "title": "Shadows of Doubt - 1.0 & Release Date Announce Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Hz2ovrxAuN0/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 126637, "name": "Announcement Trailer", "video_id": "roO6zbPEODA", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=roO6zbPEODA", "title": "Shadows of Doubt - Official Console Announce & Sharpshooter Assassin Launch Trailer